#T_SP=webanno.custom.Referent|entity|infstat
#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=Amanda Carter : That would have been about right .
#Text=It was pretty packed .
#Text=( ( WN ) )
#Text=That must have been awesome .
#Text=Amanda Carter : It was .
#Text=It was .
#Text=I guess also because it was the USA .
#Text=It was their home crowd and everything , so it was a very packed game .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) They also have a fondness for the sport .
#Text=Amanda Carter : They do .
#Text=They love basketball .
#Text=But Atlanta again was done very well .

#Text=Would have been nice to get the medal , ‘ cause I think we sort of had bigger expectations of ourselves at that point , ‘ cause we were n't the new kids on the block at that point but still finished fourth .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) They kept on saying in London that the Gliders have never won .
#Text=Amanda Carter : We 've never won a gold , no .
#Text=Not at World 's or Paralympics .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) So that was Atlanta .
#Text=Then there was another tournament , the 1998 Gold Cup .
#Text=Amanda Carter : Yes .
#Text=Which was the World Championships held in Sydney .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) How did we go in that ?
#Text=Amanda Carter : Third .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) But that qualified ... no , wait , we did n't need to qualify ...
#Text=Amanda Carter : We did n't need to qualify .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) You were the second leading scorer in the event , with thirty points scored for the competition .
#Text=Amanda Carter : Yes .
#Text=Which was unusual for a low pointer .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) In basketball , some of the low pointers do pretty well .
#Text=Amanda Carter : Yeah , but in those days I guess it was more unusual for a low pointer to be more a scorer .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) I notice the scores seem lower than the ones in London .
#Text=Amanda Carter : Yes .
#Text=I think over time the women 's game has developed .
#Text=Girls have got stronger and they 're competing against guys .
#Text=Training has got better , and all sorts of things .
#Text=So teams have just got better .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) How often do the Gliders get together ?
#Text=It seems that you are all scattered all over the country normally .
#Text=Amanda Carter : Yes .
#Text=I mean we 've got currently three in Perth , four in Melbourne , four in New South Wales , and one in Brisbane out of the twelve that were in London .
#Text=But the squad is bigger again .
#Text=We usually get together probably every six or eight weeks .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) That 's reasonably often .
#Text=Amanda Carter : Cost-wise it 's expensive to get us all together .

#Text=What we sometimes do is tack a camp on to the Women 's League , when we 're mostly all together anyway , no matter where it is , and we might stay a couple of extra days in order to train together .
#Text=But generally if we come into camp it would be at the AIS .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) I did n't see you training in Sydney this time ... then you went over to ...
